gov.anl.ipns.ViewTools.Components.ViewControls
Interface ISceneController

All Known Implementing Classes:
AltAzController, SceneController
public interface ISceneController

A ViewController object controls the observers position for one or more GL_Panel objects. Derived classes implement various interfaces to allow the user to modify the position.
